## 12. Frameworks-first для CLI

| Language | Framework |
|---|---|
| **Rust** | `clap` (de facto), `argh`, `structopt` (deprecated → `clap`) |
| **Go** | `cobra` (gh, kubectl, hugo use), `urfave/cli`, `kingpin` |
| **Python** | `click`, `typer` (modern, type hints), `argparse` (stdlib) |
| **Node.js** | `commander`, `yargs`, `cac`, `meow` |
| **C / C++** | `getopt_long` (POSIX), `cxxopts` |
| **Shell** | `getopts` (POSIX), `getopt -o` (GNU enhanced) |

### 12.1. Не пишем сами

| Категория | Готовое |
|---|---|
| Argument parsing | clap / cobra / click / commander |
| Subcommand structure | framework-built-in |
| Help generation | framework-built-in |
| Completions (bash/zsh/fish) | framework-built-in |
| Progress bars | `indicatif` (Rust), `tqdm` (Python), `progress` (Go) |
| Colors / styling | `termcolor` / `colored` (Rust), `colorama` (Python), `chalk` (Node) |
| Tables в output | `tabwriter` (Go), `tabulate` (Python), `comfy-table` (Rust) |
| JSON output | language-built-in |

---

## 13. Дистрибуция

- **Package managers:** Homebrew (macOS), apt / dnf (Linux), winget / chocolatey (Windows), pkg (BSD)
- **Cross-platform:** `cargo install`, `go install`, `npm i -g`, `pipx install`
- **Containers:** Docker / OCI image (для tools with system dependencies)
- **GitHub Releases:** pre-built binaries (cross-compile через goreleaser / cargo-dist)

Принципы:

- Single static binary где возможно (no runtime dependencies)
- Reproducible builds (готовые в CI)
- Code signing для macOS / Windows (если distrib outside store)

---

## 14. CLI-specific checklist

В дополнение к `ui-style-guide-base.md` § 7:

- [ ] `--help` / `-h` обязательно для каждой subcommand
- [ ] `--version` показывает версию
- [ ] All flags имеют long form (`--flag`)
- [ ] Exit codes документированы (0 / 1 / 2 минимум)
- [ ] stdout pipe-friendly при не-TTY (no headers/colors/spinners)
- [ ] `--json` / machine-readable mode
- [ ] `--quiet` / `-q` suppression
- [ ] Color respects `NO_COLOR` + `--no-color` + isatty detect
- [ ] Color не единственный носитель информации
- [ ] Interactive prompts только в TTY + `--yes` для skipping
- [ ] Real-time output (flush'нут, не buffered)
- [ ] SIGINT / SIGTERM graceful shutdown
- [ ] Config файл в XDG Base Directory
- [ ] Env vars с prefix `MYTOOL_`
- [ ] Errors конкретны + actionable next step
- [ ] Typo suggestions для subcommands
- [ ] Shell completions (bash/zsh/fish)
- [ ] Man pages (для serious tools)
